column5: Hello everyone- Thank you for accepting me into the forum.  Love fishing and love the outdoors. My area of expertise is generally in the Land 'o' Lakes region so if anyone is venturing out that way targeting a certain species then let me know and I would be glad to help. Thanks again
Welcome to the board thank you for joining and offering you help;   Art
